{"tid":1135110,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【兩個故】1. [甜]已經綁好miss了 2. [古風]漢代戰歌","createTime":"2019-05-02T06:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T16:10:05.000Z","uid":170630,"like":13,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c03eebe8b380fa1c073499b394775212575655bb","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:04:47.000Z","msg":"想寫兩個故，一個甜故，一個武俠故，又唔想分開放，希望兩個故都有人睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f07866cfbf1a1af598fac0cdbd7624f64a9196","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"甜故先<br />\n[已經綁好miss了]<br />\n<br />\n***<br />\n<br />\n電話響了，我依依不捨地暫停手機播放的av，接聽了電話。<br />\n<br />\n「喂，找誰？」<br />\n<br />\n「你這個壞學生！」<br />\n<br />\n天呀！這是英文miss的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n是那個靚女miss呢！像女大學生一樣的純情女miss，卻個心狠手辣，嘴巴又串的臭婆娘。<br />\n<br />\n「臭婆娘，我正在看AV，別妨礙我！」我當然不敢這麼說了。<br />\n<br />\n「Miss，有甚麼事？」<br />\n<br />\n「你已經半個月沒有上學了，作為班主任，校長要我查查是甚麼回事！」<br />\n<br />\n「半個月不上學而已，我很有錢，不上學有何大不了？」我沒有這樣說。<br />\n<br />\n「唉，我家出了點事，很難解釋。」<br />\n<br />\n「出事了嗎？要我上來看一看嗎？」靚女miss說，順帶一提，她是教英文的，應該去過外國留學，應該吃過不少洋腸。<br />\n<br />\n「上來？甚麼意思。」<br />\n<br />\n「miss來做個家訪，看看有沒有可以幫忙的地方。」<br />\n<br />\n原來是上門做&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n家訪。<br />\n<br />\n我很有錢，有樓，自己一個住，學校不少人知。<br />\n<br />\n這個女miss，難道是看中了我的錢？<br />\n<br />\n「唉，這樣嗎，說不定Miss你真的幫得到我。」<br />\n<br />\n「那我就來了哦，順便把你的功課都帶來，指點你一下吧，呵呵。」<br />\n<br />\n噢，miss要來了，我一定要做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n***<br />\n<br />\n兩日後。<br />\n<br />\n「叮噹。」<br />\n<br />\nMiss就站在門外，她穿了怎樣的裝扮呢？會是上課時穿的黑絲高跟鞋嗎？<br />\n<br />\n這樣的話，我就要把黑絲撕開，攻擊暴露的地方！<br />\n<br />\n這個女人一定有不軌的企圖，我已經做好反擊準備了。<br />\n<br />\n我在門眼處一看，竟看到一個純情的鄰家女孩。<br />\n<br />\n呀！是清純多情的女子大生呢。就像那些努力讀書，而又渴望出pool的女子大生一樣。<br />\n<br />\nMiss穿了小熱褲，四肢暴露出來，還綁了個馬尾頭。這身裝扮使她年輕數歲，大約二十出頭。<br />\n<br />\n根本就是來援交的。<br />\n<br />\n我裝出個睡眼惺忪的樣子，打開門。<br />\n<br />\n「唔&hellip;&hellip;miss&hellip;&hellip;你好&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\nMiss忍著笑走進來，她雙眼彎彎的，很有青春的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n也是多虧了她，使我對女同學都失去興趣。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，功課不多嗎？」她帶著個名牌手提袋，看來裝不下多少功課。<br />\n<br />\nMiss回頭看我一眼，便走入了客廳，在我的沙發上坐下，不斷打量四周的家具。<br />\n<br />\n「男同學，你的書桌在哪？」<br />\n<br />\n「在那哦，miss，很久沒有做了呢。」<br />\n<br />\n很久沒有做&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n功課了。<br />\n<br />\n「那就要努力做多一點了。」<br />\n<br />\n「我先沖茶給你喝吧，miss坐好。」<br />\n<br />\n我走入廚房，取出預先準備好的手銬和麻繩，嘻嘻，miss，走著瞧吧！<br />\n<br />\n廚房有一部閉路電視，可以看到客廳的miss，不看猶可，一看真是大不了。<br />\n<br />\nMiss竟在客廳把衣服都脫光，還靜靜地不做出任何聲響。<br />\n<br />\n她伸手入手提袋內，取出不知甚麼，便在客廳的鏡子面前欣賞自己的身材。<br />\n<br />\n哎喲，我只看到miss的玉背，白滑的屁股，正面呀我要正面。<br />\n<br />\n看來miss是準備給我一個驚喜呢。<br />\n<br />\n我看見miss又在角落放好自己的手機，接著竟然走向我的書桌，在那裡上上下下的看。<br />\n<br />\n看來是時候了，我於是放輕腳步，隱藏氣息，從背後欺近光屁股，miss的壞手就在我的抽屜內翻來翻去。<br />\n<br />\n我也準備好把她翻來翻去了。<br />\n<br />\n嘿！<br />\n<br />\n我成功把miss的手銬住，她尖叫一聲，一物掉落地上。<br />\n<br />\n竟然是一把刀？<br />\n<br />\nMiss剛才從手提袋內拿的竟然是一把刀？<br />\n<br />\n被銬著的手上，卻握著一大把鈔票。<br />\n<br />\n當然是我的錢了。<br />\n<br />\nMiss慌亂之下，手中的錢也掉下來。<br />\n<br />\n她又踢又拉，仍掙脫不了手銬。<br />\n<br />\n我比她更慌張。<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼miss會帶了一把刀，還拿了我的錢？<br />\n<br />\n我無暇欣賞miss慌亂的裸體與表情，把刀拾走後，便打開她的手提袋看。<br />\n<br />\n哇！居然還有一雙手套，抹布，還有其他不知名的犯罪工具。根本沒有功課。<br />\n<br />\n取看她的手機，原來是在拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n「同學&hellip;&hellip;」miss見東窗事發，呆怔著不說話。<br />\n<br />\n那把刀，是用來殺我的。<br />\n<br />\n「記過&hellip;&hellip;記過！你攻擊老師！」miss尚在狡辯。<br />\n<br />\n「miss&hellip;&hellip;你不是來做家訪的。」<br />\n<br />\n「不對，老師是來探訪你的，你為甚麼把老師扣著？還搶走老師的物品？這樣是不對的，快道歉，道歉，把我放了，就罰少一點。」<br />\n<br />\nMiss猶自擺出校內的威嚴。<br />\n<br />\n我用力在她的屁股一拍。<br />\n<br />\nMiss的屁股便彈來彈去。<br />\n<br />\n我蹲在miss的美腿後，掐她的大腿肉。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，你忘了現在自己一絲不掛吧？明明是差恥的時候，還在給我耍威嚴？」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯！放手！你傷害老師，還把我的衣服扒光！」<br />\n<br />\n「扒光？」我向她展示出閉路電視的影像。<br />\n<br />\nMiss呆了，曼麗的身材僵硬得像死屍一樣。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，你根本就不懷好意，你完了。」<br />\n<br />\nMiss搖搖頭不說話，她的眼珠突出，突然崩潰流淚。<br />\n<br />\n呼，想不到色心反而救了自己一命。<br />\n<br />\n現在到我教育miss的時候了。"},{"pid":"1eb5a390ae91e0fe3281a5a088bc531865936cf1","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:56:54.000Z","msg":"我先用麻繩把miss綁好，使她做了個跪地同時雙膝張開的姿勢，手就綁到背後，便扣著她的髮束，一把拉下去，使miss披頭散髮。<br />\n<br />\n過程中miss不斷說話狡辯，都給我一一無視了。<br />\n<br />\n這時處理妥當後，miss已口乾得說不出話，只因麻繩緊結而發出痛苦的低吟，呼吸也變得粗躁。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，你可以說話了，我現在開始聽。」<br />\n<br />\n「嗄&hellip;&hellip;嗄&hellip;&hellip;我不說了，你快放開老師&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「miss，你口渴嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n她疲憊地點頭。<br />\n<br />\n於是我沖了碗茶出來，瓷器碰地的聲音清脆。<br />\n<br />\n我把茶餵向miss，她要飲的時候，我說。<br />\n<br />\n「事先聲音，茶有春藥，你還要喝嗎？」<br />\n<br />\nMiss合上嘴巴。<br />\n<br />\n於是我把茶放在地上，她緊盯著茶，呼吸愈來愈粗重。<br />\n<br />\n半小時後，我再向她餵茶，miss貪婪地把茶喝下。<br />\n<br />\n吃了春藥後的miss全身泛紅，眼神呆呆滯滯的，連腰也軟下來了。<br />\n<br />\n我用手輕撫miss的面龐，她的臉嫩又滑，飽受護膚品滋潤呢，一拍下來不少姻脂粉。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，飲茶後好點了嘛？」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯。」miss點點頭。<br />\n<br />\n「那我現在要開始問話了，不把事情弄清楚，我睡不著。」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯。」miss嗯得很溫柔。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，功課呢？你說要帶功課給我做，為甚麼沒有？」<br />\n<br />\nMiss扭扭拐拐的不說話，我唯有在她的幼腰一抓。<br />\n<br />\nMiss笑嘻嘻的，便把話吐出來。"},{"pid":"2fc31c9ae529870b338352c39cb2b66fcb3e57ff","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"「沒有功課，那是騙人的，miss上來只是為了探你。」<br />\n<br />\n捏一捏她的鼻子，又問。<br />\n<br />\n「探我甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n「嘻嘻，你知道你不上學，學校的人怎樣說你嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n學校的人？<br />\n<br />\n閉上眼，浮現一個個生硬的人影，我認得他們的樣子，有俊有醜，有男有女，有老有少，以前經常出現。<br />\n<br />\n我卻一直不知道他們是誰。<br />\n<br />\n他們說了甚麼話呢？<br />\n<br />\n難不成對一個輟學的貴公子產生興趣了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我的同學們，難道對我這個影子學生感到好奇，不時討論我嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「學校的人怎樣說？」<br />\n<br />\n「甚麼也沒有說。」<br />\n<br />\n甚麼也沒有說&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「你不在，沒有人說，甚至沒有人察覺，少了一個人，他們不知不覺，還要更加高興！」miss淫笑著說。<br />\n<br />\n不知為何，心像被槌了一下。<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n「所以說，老師見沒有人關心你，所以想要給些愛你，男同學，給老師鬆綁吧。」<br />\n<br />\n是的，miss明明一片好心，專程來看望我，我怎可以綁著她？<br />\n<br />\n「對不起，miss，是我太敏感。」<br />\n<br />\n於是我伸手便要解開繩索，miss在我的手上香了一口，然後又吃吃淫笑。<br />\n<br />\n呀，彎彎的眼，來關心我的大姐姐miss，很溫柔呀。"},{"pid":"8c823b980b3c4ef3514f6da03bd296f7737c2901","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b97c472936a32ab8fb877ebfa43db51f7efe4c2","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c823b980b3c4ef3514f6da03bd296f7737c2901","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc09b22b84a482c0a7b209130f1967a4d967d46e","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b97c472936a32ab8fb877ebfa43db51f7efe4c2","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c823b980b3c4ef3514f6da03bd296f7737c2901","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:36:46.000Z","msg":"我睇緊個喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd0a79eb079d8ca23cfcbcb16feee0a8e3c43eb","tid":1135110,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"分開post啦"},{"pid":"84cfab5a8ef4514d6ce66bb4450f93c34168b65c","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc09b22b84a482c0a7b209130f1967a4d967d46e","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b97c472936a32ab8fb877ebfa43db51f7efe4c2","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c823b980b3c4ef3514f6da03bd296f7737c2901","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:36:46.000Z","msg":"我睇緊個喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace21db37c8f6e22e160de0e349a12e528e776c6","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd0a79eb079d8ca23cfcbcb16feee0a8e3c43eb","tid":1135110,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"分開post啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"重新開過？"},{"pid":"4700abc6611d00696cefc8b7d3f37580e7681ce9","tid":1135110,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace21db37c8f6e22e160de0e349a12e528e776c6","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd0a79eb079d8ca23cfcbcb16feee0a8e3c43eb","tid":1135110,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"分開post啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"重新開過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"甜故繼續喺度post<br />\n武俠新開一個"},{"pid":"2b6f2c2ed4005f19ae15ffb4ecb672b8739aeeee","tid":1135110,"uid":111069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"點解無啦啦會除曬衫褲"},{"pid":"a16178bb2acfc55c8e81edee05c902ae68db6416","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b6f2c2ed4005f19ae15ffb4ecb672b8739aeeee","tid":1135110,"uid":111069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"點解無啦啦會除曬衫褲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"仙人跳"},{"pid":"a5dbe9962617be76653256992a2b24f95b546ff6","tid":1135110,"uid":235948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"未睇名已經認得啲文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c215cf04b148d97753481c7d919219b1c864ebcf","tid":1135110,"uid":237914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5dbe9962617be76653256992a2b24f95b546ff6","tid":1135110,"uid":235948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"未睇名已經認得啲文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"啲文痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92f2a961e2c13f0e9da43d184a4c52f1c2de929","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"地上有利刀。<br />\n<br />\n對了。<br />\n<br />\n我心一寒，退出兩步。<br />\n<br />\n嗚。<br />\n<br />\n差點給這個美女騙了。<br />\n<br />\n「男同學，快幫老師鬆綁呀。讓老師關心你，給愛你。」<br />\n<br />\n我用力搖頭，擺脫大暈其浪。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，你關心我，為甚麼帶刀？你脫光衣服是要給我溫柔也能說通，但為甚麼藏刀呢？」<br />\n<br />\n此時春藥還在發作，miss傾著頭吹氣，口水成了一條線流下來。<br />\n<br />\n她看著我一直笑，千嬌百媚，就是不說話。<br />\n<br />\n因為她想不到託詞。<br />\n<br />\n因為那把刀是用來殺我的。<br />\n<br />\n「miss&hellip;&hellip;你還是&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「No，老師只是關心你，但老師也有點怕你，因為你平時上課十分陰沉，現在你又不上課，老師又不知你變成甚麼樣子。」<br />\n<br />\n「老師帶把武器防身，是要在必要時阻止你傷害人，還有傷害自己。」<br />\n<br />\n「老師帶點防備&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「老師帶點準備，只是為了保護你，以免你犯罪。」<br />\n<br />\n「老師只是為你好。」<br />\n<br />\n我蹲下看地，miss便在我的頭髮上輕吻。<br />\n<br />\n絲絲的溫柔透入我的頭腦內。<br />\n<br />\n好舒服呀，一股暖流使我雞皮疙瘩，miss笑得真溫柔。<br />\n<br />\n於是我伸手又要解開miss的繩索。<br />\n<br />\n「miss關心我嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「關心。」她用最溫柔的語氣說。<br />\n<br />\n「miss愛我嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「愛。」她擺出最慈愛的表情。<br />\n<br />\n我要解開miss。<br />\n<br />\n才不。<br />\n<br />\n我縮回手。<br />\n<br />\n「那又怎樣？」我說。<br />\n<br />\n「我只是想要強姦你。」我說。<br />\n<br />\nMiss終於露出陰險的表情，便又恢復微笑。<br />\n<br />\n於是我取出震蛋，按摩器，還有小鞭鞭和蠟燭。<br />\n<br />\n準備開始嚴刑拷問。"},{"pid":"94e0d208b6fb4c57c49e02b7d93fa94c768bf487","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7a3632776af5bb2adcace3d0cccca2f04b900f","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"在拷問之前，當然要先幫miss潤潤喉。<br />\n<br />\n於是我拿出一合鮮奶，餵miss。<br />\n<br />\n她咕嚕咕嚕就喝下去了，滿足地笑了笑。<br />\n<br />\n我又給她一杯清水，又幫miss尿尿之後，便開始刑訊。<br />\n<br />\n啟動了攝影機，我繞到miss身後，輕輕抱著miss，雙手在她的乳房揉弄，miss的頸子於是扭來扭去。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，你說你要關心我是不是？」<br />\n<br />\n「是呀&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「我也要關心miss，比如這樣！」於是掐著她兩邊乳暈，又拉又掐。<br />\n<br />\n「這樣做是要幫助miss，抒發教學的壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n「唔哼哼哼。」她愉悅地笑，真不愧是成熟的大姐姐呀！<br />\n<br />\n可是，她的乳暈強硬得很，可能是因為她身經百戰，我的技術不夠，未能使乳頭腫起。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的話，為了將miss的神智摧毀，得到真相，我唯有使用作弊的方法。<br />\n<br />\n打開震蛋，對準miss的乳暈，突擊！<br />\n<br />\n「嗚啊啊！」<br />\n<br />\n乳暈快速激突，miss高興得把長腰挺起來。<br />\n<br />\n為了把雙手騰出，又使用了愛心小貼紙，把蛋蛋固定住。<br />\n<br />\nMiss像被電擊一樣，縮縮突突。<br />\n<br />\n於是我開始問話。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，請你忍耐，只要你把真相說出來，我便馬上把你放走。」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯&hellip;&hellip;好&hellip;&hellip;好&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「一， 功課呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「呀&hellip;&hellip;功課是騙你的，根本沒有人關心你的學業，嗯&hellip;&hellip;只是順口說說罷了。」<br />\n<br />\n「同學呢？你說他們更開心，是真的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯&hellip;&hellip;很可惜，是真的，正是因為他們開心，完全沒有在乎過你，miss才會想上來。」<br />\n<br />\n「校長叫的？」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯嗯，騙你的，我自己想來。」<br />\n<br />\n「哼！原來是個姣女人！」<br />\n<br />\n我取出第三顆蛋蛋，用愛心小貼貼固定在她的小粒粒上。<br />\n<br />\n便開始聽到奇怪的聲音，刺激的氣味。<br />\n<br />\nMiss開始「吐露」真相。<br />\n<br />\n黏黏的水水漏出來了。<br />\n<br />\n「你為甚麼要來？」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯&hellip;&hellip;呀&hellip;&hellip;不是說了嗎？老師愛錫你，不想讓你自己一個。」<br />\n<br />\n「哼，miss這麼狡猾，我可不相信！」<br />\n<br />\n於是我把耳貼近miss的胸口。<br />\n<br />\n把頭擠擠入奶子內，嗅著miss的乳香，還有點花香氣，miss含眼脈脈的俯視我。<br />\n<br />\n「噗通、噗通&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n唔&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nMiss的心聲。<br />\n<br />\n聽來很謙厚，不像是在說謊。"},{"pid":"ec5a25fe76c8bc48e04ded10d33a656a7be92a27","tid":1135110,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:12:40.000Z","msg":"留名加甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73697241344065140471e9438a6140a5d1706a5","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec5a25fe76c8bc48e04ded10d33a656a7be92a27","tid":1135110,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:12:40.000Z","msg":"留名加甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272e45141661d057ff5ee7509fbd473385965395","tid":1135110,"uid":2278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"正評加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14697c5c744839c93710a35dfdf3bdce7c1d52be","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"272e45141661d057ff5ee7509fbd473385965395","tid":1135110,"uid":2278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"正評加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"「哼！miss說大話！」<br />\n<br />\n「怎麼會？」<br />\n<br />\n「明明赤身裸體，心跳怎可能平靜？證明miss是一個不知羞恥的女騙子！」<br />\n<br />\n「男同學，老師對你只有關懷和愛，怎會感到羞恥？你感受不到老師的溫暖嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「溫暖？溫暖也需要證明！嘿！」<br />\n<br />\n我猛地撕開乳頭貼，miss吃痛，我便揉弄揉弄，於是張口貼著miss的奶奶。<br />\n<br />\n咬咬，舐舐。<br />\n<br />\n吮，吮。<br />\n<br />\n吮，吮。<br />\n<br />\n唔！來了！溫暖湧進口腔。<br />\n<br />\n又甜，又香。<br />\n<br />\n吮，吮。<br />\n<br />\n吮，吮。<br />\n<br />\n左一口，右一口，是溫暖的味道！<br />\n<br />\n美麗的大姐姐，miss給我的愛和溫暖！<br />\n<br />\n呀&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n咕嚕咕嚕。<br />\n<br />\n我飽餐了一頓後，miss也有點累了。<br />\n<br />\n於是我改變了miss綁綁的姿勢，使她可以平躺下來。"},{"pid":"76b1fdd2e882c22b2548655fdc0cce19381d01b1","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"272e45141661d057ff5ee7509fbd473385965395","tid":1135110,"uid":2278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"正評加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"你啦，就是你啦，兩百字送給這位先生，來來來。"},{"pid":"4cdcd34022e22acde2d8fb274c12c65800943102","tid":1135110,"uid":143730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"太早入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持！加速！"},{"pid":"f48c7f2eea4348e6706e0605428b79d03d291b93","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4cdcd34022e22acde2d8fb274c12c65800943102","tid":1135110,"uid":143730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"太早入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持！加速！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"把她拖到床上，當成人肉攬枕一樣抱著。<br />\n<br />\n好一會後，miss終於忍不住問。<br />\n<br />\n「同學，還不解開老師？」<br />\n<br />\n「miss愛我，我也愛miss呀。」<br />\n<br />\n我扒在miss身上壓著miss，她比我高一個頭，所以正好枕在乳暈上。<br />\n<br />\n我坐在miss身上，開始親吻，又臉親到肩、再親到乳頭、親肚臍、親到下陰。<br />\n<br />\n又大幅度上上下下狂舐miss的美長腿。<br />\n<br />\nMiss嗯嗯的不依。<br />\n<br />\n「同學，愛不是這樣的，愛是care，即是互相關懷，不需要&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\nMiss說不下去，因為她的舌頭已給我吮實。<br />\n<br />\nYum，hum。<br />\n<br />\n我吸去miss的口液，又再吐回miss口內。<br />\n<br />\n「這是我愛miss的方法。」<br />\n<br />\nMiss給我愛得發抖了。<br />\n<br />\n我叉著miss的頸子。<br />\n<br />\n「Miss，你自投羅網，怪不得我愛愛miss。」<br />\n<br />\nMiss見自己的演技都被我識破，激動得咬牙切齒。"},{"pid":"7bceaa0b69eb58e539ae902edc8f49662db84e07","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4cdcd34022e22acde2d8fb274c12c65800943102","tid":1135110,"uid":143730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"太早入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持！加速！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"前面送了兩百字，現在再送你兩百字啦，一百一百的送出去，不用客氣啦，大家都是朋依友啦，出聲就對啦。哦。"},{"pid":"83950e5fe661ae19b5a19002303f0cf3e7a2fbfd","tid":1135110,"uid":247372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"仲有冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4ccac8d567612383b5a2ae225f8687f573a9f2","tid":1135110,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"扑未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32d861130e636992f30f39bd505ca9a6df9b7a2","tid":1135110,"uid":152815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9d0bfd8c74cea092d939baf76b20a90958b19a7f","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"「我的乖乖miss，別瀲動哦，生氣的樣子可不好看，容易變老哦。」<br />\n<br />\nMiss仍然不住發抖，我唯有取出一條冷冷的啫喱棒，對準miss的小穴，緩緩透入。<br />\n<br />\n「唔&hellip;&hellip;呀&hellip;&hellip;這是？」<br />\n<br />\n看來miss也未玩過這小玩具。<br />\n<br />\n於是我一下子加速，啫喱棒便直搗入深處。<br />\n<br />\n冷冷的啫喱棒成功使miss冷靜下來，她僵硬了，目瞪口呆，看著上方不知在想甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n我又再扒在miss身上，直到她變回柔軟。<br />\n<br />\n在她耳邊輕輕道。<br />\n<br />\n「miss，舒服嗎？」<br />\n<br />\nMiss吞了一口口水，閉上眼睛卻沒有回應我。<br />\n<br />\n「Miss，我想要學習，我們現在學習可不可以？」<br />\n<br />\nMiss還是不答我，於是我掀開miss的眼睛，迫她看我。<br />\n<br />\n我再香一口。<br />\n<br />\n「Miss，『同學們有其他問題嗎？』，快點這樣問。」<br />\n<br />\nMiss不理我，我便取出按摩器。<br />\n<br />\n嘿！<br />\n<br />\n在miss的小粒粒處一觸，miss的腰彈了起來。<br />\n<br />\n「快說，不然就讓你更舒服。」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯，嗯！Do you have any questions？」<br />\n<br />\n「Miss, I have a question.」<br />\n<br />\n「為甚麼miss會關心我？你平時不是笑我大雄嗎？為甚麼會忽然改變態度？」<br />\n<br />\n「because&hellip; because&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「別支支吾吾！」我又再襲擊miss的私處，她悶聲劇震，像坐電椅一樣。<br />\n<br />\n「嗄&hellip;&hellip;嗄&hellip;&hellip;」我停下按摩棒，miss抖氣說不出話。<br />\n<br />\n於是我在她耳邊說道。<br />\n<br />\n「讓我猜猜好不好？」<br />\n<br />\nMiss合上眼點點頭。<br />\n<br />\n「Miss上來，是想要我的錢對不對？」<br />\n<br />\nMiss不應。<br />\n<br />\n「Miss因為知道我是個邊緣人，發生甚麼事也沒有人理的可憐蟲。」<br />\n<br />\n「因為我自己一個人住，就算發生了甚麼意外，一時三刻也沒有人會知道，偏生我又是條大水魚。」<br />\n<br />\n「而miss又剛好是個Bitch，所以想來混水摸魚是不是？」<br />\n<br />\nMiss扭扭拐拐，於是我又擠入miss的奶內聆聽她的心跳聲。<br />\n<br />\n是羞恥的心跳呢！想不到miss也會感到羞恥。<br />\n<br />\n我繼續說。<br />\n<br />\n「因為miss是來做壞事的，自然不會留下任何線索，讓其他人知道你來過這裡。」<br />\n<br />\n我再聽聽miss的心跳，看來我說對了。<br />\n<br />\n「嘻嘻！」我邪笑。<br />\n<br />\n我也覺得自己實在笑得很怪，我也未聽過這樣的笑聲。<br />\n<br />\n我道。<br />\n<br />\n「正因為miss沒有留下線索，嘻嘻！」<br />\n<br />\n「所以我對你做任何事，也沒有人會知！」<br />\n<br />\nMiss的心跳加快了，我的舌頭也加快了。<br />\n<br />\n「很香很香！Miss的味道很不錯！」<br />\n<br />\n「難得我這個邊緣人得到愛了，我不會讓愛白白流走的。」<br />\n<br />\n「Miss，你的真正意圖是甚麼我也不理了。」<br />\n<br />\n「因為我愛上miss了。」<br />\n<br />\n「我愛miss，我愛miss。」<br />\n<br />\n「Miss我愛你，我愛你。」<br />\n<br />\n「我不愛讓愛人離開的。」<br />\n<br />\n此時門鈴響起，嚇得我呢。"},{"pid":"d547693949b640a06285a73d78948840ccbcda2f","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83950e5fe661ae19b5a19002303f0cf3e7a2fbfd","tid":1135110,"uid":247372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"仲有冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635adb0886111c6918189424cdc960a3044c5667","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c4ccac8d567612383b5a2ae225f8687f573a9f2","tid":1135110,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"扑未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2067d7cd47f2921bb9cc21e769cfe840e3652f5b","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f32d861130e636992f30f39bd505ca9a6df9b7a2","tid":1135110,"uid":152815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2addd9fcd1a8fa9a71363dc171a3b66af2d9a5","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"瀲動=&gt;激動"},{"pid":"ac67d85dd43602a768bf077afc0607f795efd7a8","tid":1135110,"uid":162177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69b2ba3412b5c1b9091911892852246977575700","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"今晚都夜囉，抱住miss訓覺囉"},{"pid":"2a107246cbab24ec925258e7757921ffd32d7428","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:01:45.000Z","msg":"我想到早前叫的外賣，便穿好褲子，走了出去。<br />\n<br />\n打開門，便見到熟悉的外賣仔。<br />\n<br />\n「少爺，一共兩百蚊。」<br />\n<br />\n「好了，明明只有一百多，剩下來的你拿去買零食吧。」<br />\n<br />\n外賣仔笑了笑，這就是他叫我少爺的原因。<br />\n<br />\n「救命呀！有人強姦我呀！」miss竟在這時大叫。<br />\n<br />\n外賣仔面色一變。<br />\n<br />\n噢！甚麼嘛？<br />\n<br />\n我想不到處理的方法，唯有勃起回應。<br />\n<br />\n「呀，那個，我在&hellip;&hellip;」我支支吾吾。<br />\n<br />\n「呀！少爺年紀輕輕，真厲害呢？」<br />\n<br />\n外賣仔吃吃淫笑，便退了出去。<br />\n<br />\n我關上門。<br />\n<br />\n這個miss！<br />\n<br />\n我馬上衝回房，騎在miss身上。<br />\n<br />\n她尖叫一聲，我把miss反轉了後，便拿出小鞭鞭。<br />\n<br />\n「劈、劈、劈。」<br />\n<br />\n於是我坐在miss的背上。<br />\n<br />\n她抽抽涕涕不語。<br />\n<br />\n「Miss，我雖然愛你，但也不要得意忘形了，你這匹母馬還需要馴化。」<br />\n<br />\n我便裝成騎馬的樣子，在miss背上搖來搖去。<br />\n<br />\n我把miss再翻轉的時候，她已經不成人形。<br />\n<br />\n我這才發現啫喱棒還在小穴內，怪不得miss受不了，便一把抽起啫喱棒。<br />\n<br />\n哎喲！<br />\n<br />\n嘩啦嘩啦。<br />\n<br />\n「嗯！我去了！」<br />\n<br />\n突如其來一陣雲雨，我躲避不及，吃了個正。<br />\n<br />\nMiss的水水顏射到我的全身上。<br />\n<br />\n哎呀床裖地板甚麼的全濕濕了。<br />\n<br />\n濕濕。<br />\n<br />\n不要。<br />\n<br />\n都濕濕濕濕了。"},{"pid":"4e8843c2b535a015efbb4017030c12df27116a86","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac67d85dd43602a768bf077afc0607f795efd7a8","tid":1135110,"uid":162177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:12:27.000Z","msg":"大力一點"},{"pid":"af2424fc35ee3390e6db7aa0c1fae7d5374aa43a","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea4b820498f79429f5c23dfbbf1b64d3a0f2a52","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af2424fc35ee3390e6db7aa0c1fae7d5374aa43a","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"真人真事，絕無虛構"},{"pid":"5837834bbf32756add9521e2f0928cfca3d2bc2c","tid":1135110,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aea4b820498f79429f5c23dfbbf1b64d3a0f2a52","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af2424fc35ee3390e6db7aa0c1fae7d5374aa43a","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"真人真事，絕無虛構"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8639475767577dc4e1103f7f8ab73983b87b349","tid":1135110,"uid":237914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aea4b820498f79429f5c23dfbbf1b64d3a0f2a52","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af2424fc35ee3390e6db7aa0c1fae7d5374aa43a","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"真人真事，絕無虛構"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"我又屌"},{"pid":"1c5ef3f278ae19168aad288a86d0ec116896e56c","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8639475767577dc4e1103f7f8ab73983b87b349","tid":1135110,"uid":237914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aea4b820498f79429f5c23dfbbf1b64d3a0f2a52","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af2424fc35ee3390e6db7aa0c1fae7d5374aa43a","tid":1135110,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"真人真事，絕無虛構"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"我又屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"miss是我的"},{"pid":"3cec2dca18efe4ce5e8c5ab5f48166d907e8192f","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"這就是所謂的春風化雨嗎？<br />\n<br />\n回過神來，miss的吐露還有餘陣。<br />\n<br />\n不知為何，我精神一爽之後，突然又充滿勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n小穴穴看來，有點吸引。<br />\n<br />\n我吸！<br />\n<br />\n便吸咐在小穴穴外。<br />\n<br />\n「那裡很髒！同學！馬上停止。」<br />\n<br />\n誰了停啦！<br />\n<br />\n我吮。<br />\n<br />\n吮、吮。<br />\n<br />\n吮、吮。<br />\n<br />\n吮、吮、吮、吮。<br />\n<br />\n是勇氣！勇氣都進來了。勇氣的咸咸爽爽的，很好吃呢！<br />\n<br />\n我把miss帶到飯廳，幫miss坐好。<br />\n<br />\n這時候的miss口水、淚水還有小淫水都漏乾了，所以看起來又點瘦。<br />\n<br />\n所以，現在便是幫miss補充營養的時候！<br />\n<br />\n「Miss，外賣到了，有湯有飯！我們一起吃吧！」<br />\n<br />\n我吃一口，餵miss，用同一的餐具。<br />\n<br />\nMiss餓了，胃口很好，吃得也很開心，她表情呆呆滯滯，看起來已停止了思考。<br />\n<br />\n很久沒有人陪我吃飯了，是夜是我人生中最快樂的一晚。<br />\n<br />\n和miss一起洗完澡後，我們便一起上床睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n渡過美滿的良宵，我重拾對生命的熱誠。<br />\n<br />\n因為miss的愛和關懷，使我得到重回校園的勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n第二天早，我當miss的奶水是早餐，吃了個飽。<br />\n<br />\n「Miss，我上學了。」<br />\n<br />\n我不待miss回答，便背上書包出門。<br />\n<br />\n因為miss的到來，使我脫出自閉的囚籠，使我的思想由負面變得富有陽光。<br />\n<br />\nMiss啟發我，讓我知道不是一個人！在學校裡也一定有很多像miss一樣關心我的人在！<br />\n<br />\n呀！有純情的女同學呀，關心我的學長學姊，還有春風化雨，教育我的良師，和我一起共渡青春的死黨。<br />\n<br />\nMiss謝謝你呀。<br />\n<br />\n呀！美好的校園，我來了！<br />\n<br />\n像是卸下了心頭大石一樣，背包變得很輕，我跑向美好的校園。"},{"pid":"f8b8f1ef4bc01c16ac96f78c608e6aeb651752bc","tid":1135110,"uid":237914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"完？"},{"pid":"1953dd44544fba19c27f7b2f2d7b0b2112d8743b","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:50:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完</span></span>"},{"pid":"cbe5021291e04ea37a08192678538ccff0693445","tid":1135110,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"最重要既過程你唔寫埋出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d2a3540f0963c486c82f54b6bcbd16e5888333","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbe5021291e04ea37a08192678538ccff0693445","tid":1135110,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"最重要既過程你唔寫埋出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:14:22.000Z","msg":"陣間寫"},{"pid":"3dec1d65b26708fbb0f39b9f5dd61c397245bdea","tid":1135110,"uid":170630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"現在是下午一點半，我在快餐店買了一杯雪糕。<br />\n<br />\n我需要雪糕來冷靜，現在我甚至連書包也沒有帶在身旁。<br />\n<br />\n早上時，那個風紀隊長，她一看見我走入校門，就指著我。<br />\n<br />\n「快！捉！住！那！個！人！」<br />\n<br />\n我還來不及說話，已被數個高年級的風紀圍住。<br />\n<br />\n「這！個！人！冒！充！我！校！學！生！圖！謀！不！軌！馬！上！報！警！」<br />\n<br />\n「風紀姐姐，我是來上學的，我是這間中學的！」<br />\n<br />\n「別！騙！人！我！每！天！早！上！都！在！校！園！開！崗！根！本！沒！有！見！過！你！」<br />\n<br />\n「你未見過我關我甚麼事？」<br />\n<br />\n於是我轉身打算扭過她。<br />\n<br />\n她伸手扯著我的書包，我便捉著她的手用力甩開。<br />\n<br />\n「哇！」<br />\n<br />\n風紀湧上來，我被按在地上動彈不得。<br />\n<br />\n「這！個！人！剛！才！用！咸！豬！手！非！禮！我！快！點！報！警！」<br />\n<br />\n「我哪有非禮你！哎呀你按得我很痛！」<br />\n<br />\n「閉！路！電！視！都！拍！下！來！了！你！因！為！好！色！摸！我！的！手！」<br />\n<br />\n唉，就是這樣，後來我展示出學生證。<br />\n<br />\n她才給我進入校園，還是訓了我一頓。<br />\n<br />\n還說甚麼︰<br />\n<br />\n「儀！容！不！潔！沒！有！腰！帶！也！沒！有！校！呔！頭！髮！過！長！」<br />\n<br />\n又把我訓了一番。<br />\n<br />\n我再回到課室的時候，堂已上了一半。<br />\n<br />\n在這種時機走入去，情況可想而知。<br />\n<br />\n在體育課的時候，因為我沒有帶體育服，所以也決定不下操場了，就坐在課室睡午睏。<br />\n<br />\n迷迷糊糊的時候，有一個人走入班房。<br />\n<br />\n那東西拂來拂去，很是搶眼，是條馬尾，我擦亮眼睛，入目一個小小的女人人影。<br />\n<br />\n她翻找著書包，沒有發現我，於是我偷偷關上課室門。<br />\n<br />\n我想起來了，這個女人名字叫做小柔。<br />\n<br />\n她沒有身材，不算最漂亮的那種，但眼總帶著吸引人的笑意，那種眼睛望誰都一樣，天生便很吃香。<br />\n<br />\n她也說不上是來者不拒的人。<br />\n<br />\n只是，沒有很明確的拒絕吧，所以她也有不少曖昧的姘頭。<br />\n<br />\n常常有狗公在背後討論小柔，說她這天那天又和某某出了街。<br />\n<br />\n在旺角看到某某和小柔走入奇怪的地方之類的。<br />\n<br />\n只能說，小柔看上去很年輕，很天真。<br />\n<br />\n實際上當然是個厲害的人了。<br />\n<br />\n在小柔離開課室的時候，我偷偷欺了上去。<br />\n<br />\n朝她馬尾一抓，抓了個空，她回頭看了我一眼，便輕輕的跳出去了。<br />\n<br />\n她當然不會像那個風紀學姐一樣說我非禮她了。<br />\n<br />\n理由很簡單，小柔是個厲害的女人。<br />\n<br />\n小柔走了後，再沒有甚麼事情發生。<br />\n<br />\n午飯之後，我便決定早退。"},{"pid":"467cef62ff13aaeb000854918e5ff23b3208382b","tid":1135110,"uid":147057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"唔好再出感嘆號人啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}